    <dd>
     Jingle Bus (F)
    </dd>
   </dl>
   <article>
    <p>
     To the tune of Jingle Bells:
    </p>
    <p>
     Dashing thru the snow<br/>
     In a Bus that's Red and Grey<br/>
     Got my BN2<br/>
     Cranked up all the way ...
    </p>
    <p>
     (everybody sing!)
    </p>
    <p class="sig">
     Bob Hufford<br/>
     Transporter Search &amp; Rescue<br/>
     bhufford@mail.orion.org
    </p>
