    <p>
     Bull bars on the front,<br/>
     Bumping bucks and does,<br/>
     Add more flames onto this thread<br/>
     I'll punch you in the nose!
    </p>
    <p>
     Oh, splitty bus, splitty bus,<br/>
     Driven like a sleigh,<br/>
     Four bald tires and bailing wire<br/>
     Won't get you on your way!
    </p>
    <p>
     Oh, splitty bus, splitty bus,<br/>
     Howling from the rear,<br/>
     Add some oil or more turmoil<br/>
     Will bite you in the rear!
    </p>
    <p class="sig">
